(1, 'Technology Thema', 'IN', '1742287177_1742279379_745-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '80001', '18', '<p>Technology Thema Service&nbsp; likely refers to Thema IT Services,&nbsp;a company specializing in providing full IT support and ICT outsourcing to small and medium-sized enterprises.&nbsp;They offer a range of services, including remote and on-site IT support, web design, and more</p>', 1),
(2, 'Solar Power Thema', 'IN', '1742287650_1742279210_czNmcy1wcml2YXRlL3Jhd3BpeGVsX2ltYWdlcy93ZWJzaXRlX2NvbnRlbnQvcm01MTktbS0wMV8xLWwxazFqajl6LmpwZw-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '81001', '17', '<p>Solar Power as a Service is&nbsp;a business model that aims to make renewable energy accessible by providing solar power solutions without the need for upfront investment or complicated calculations, offering a low-risk way to access solar energy</p>', 1),
(3, 'Software Thema', 'IN', '1742287745_1742278821_ui-ux-designers-isometric-composition-with-small-people-creating-custom-design-web-site-3d-vector-illustration_1284-68939-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '82001', '16', '<p>Software Thema Service likely refers to Thema Consultants Ltd, an IT Managed Services Provider offering support services for networks, servers, databases, software, and web solutions</p>', 1),
(4, 'Real Estate Thema', 'IN', '1742287868_1742278615_3847365beb7da39d34684ae14e4b7bf5-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '83001', '15', '<p>Real Estate Thema Servicen likely refers to&nbsp;real estate-specific WordPress themes designed to help agencies and agents create professional websites for showcasing properties and managing their business.&nbsp;These themes offer features like property listings, search filters, and property</p>', 1),
(5, 'Insurance Thema', 'IN', '1742287952_1742278394_png-clipart-vehicle-insurance-health-insurance-insurance-agent-work-safety-and-health-day-text-service-thumbnail-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '84001', '14', '<p>Insurance Thema Service likely refers to&nbsp;a WordPress theme designed for insurance companies or agencies, offering features for showcasing services, managing content, and potentially integrating with insurance-related functions</p>', 1),
(6, 'Beauty Product Thema', 'IN', '1742288061_1742278277_png-transparent-assorted-brand-labeled-makeup-products-cosmetics-beauty-makeup-brush-make-up-artist-women-cosmetics-miscellaneous-women-accessories-indian-nude-women-thumbnail-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '85001', '13', '<p>According to How To Get Into Beauty Marketing - A Definitive Guide |Alpha Academy, beauty marketing is&nbsp;what a beauty marketer does is to promote a product or brand&nbsp;In other words, it&#39;s the way marketers present a beauty product or line to its consumers</p>', 1),
(7, 'Automobile Thema', 'IN', '1742288176_1742278057_Blog-Banner-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '86001', '12', '<p>Automobile Thema Service likely refers to&nbsp;themes or templates designed for websites related to car repair, service, or dealerships.&nbsp;These themes are often built on platforms like html responsive and offer features tailored for the automotive industry</p>', 1),
(8, 'Bitcoin Thema', 'IN', '1742288310_1742277840_hd-group-of-bitcoin-coins-png-704081695127103rhkbswpntw-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '87001', '11', '<p>Locate your public address on the front of your Material Bitcoin wallet.&nbsp;Scan the QR code or type the public address into a balance checker tool. Instantly see your Bitcoin balance</p>', 1),
(9, 'Travel Thema', 'IN', '1742288387_1742277616_realistic-travel-horizontal-banner-suitcases-beach-umbrellas-other-attributes-tourism-gathered-together-vector-illustration_1284-81822-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '88001', '10', '<p>Travel services&nbsp;offer professional solutions to help individuals and businesses organize, book, and manage travel, encompassing everything from flight and hotel bookings to itinerary planning and customer support</p>', 1),
(10, 'Medical Thema', 'IN', '1742288570_1742277423_set-of-bottles-tablets-pills-capsules-and-spray-png-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '89001', '9', '<p>Medical Thema Service&nbsp; likely refers to thema&nbsp; medical,&nbsp;a company offering strategic regulatory consulting services for medical and IVD devices</p>', 1),
(11, 'Health Thema', 'IN', '1742288745_1742277044_1523-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '90001', '8', '<p>Health Thema Service likely refers to&nbsp;a company or organization providing healthcare services, potentially with a focus on community or corporate wellness, based on the search results</p>', 1),
(12, 'E-commerce Thema', 'IN', '1742288828_1742276879_k-removebg-preview.png', 'fa fa-globe me-2', '91001', '7', '<p>E-commerce Thema Service likely refers to&nbsp;a service or platform that helps businesses create and manage their online stores, focusing on both the visual theme (design) and the functional aspects of e-commerce</p>', 1),
