(458, 10, 83, 'home', 'Get Medik Hand Sanitizer', '<p>GetMedik Hand Sanitizer is a powerful and effective solution designed to keep your hands germ-free and protected. Infused with 70% alcohol, it kills 99.9% of bacteria and viruses, making it ideal for daily use at home, work, or on the go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This sanitizer is quick-drying, non-sticky, and enriched with moisturizing agents to prevent dryness, ensuring your hands remain soft and hydrated. Its portable packaging allows easy application anytime, anywhere&mdash;whether before meals, after touching surfaces, or during travel.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743411831_baby-img.jpg', 1, NULL, 0),
(459, 10, 83, 'service', 'GetMedik Hand Sanitizer: Ultimate Protection for Clean Hands', '<p>An alcohol-free bar, also known as a temperance bar, sober bar, or dry bar, is a social space that serves non-alcoholic beverages like mocktails, alcohol-free beer, and soft drinks, providing an alternative to traditional bars without alcohol.&nbsp;</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743412072_soap.jpg', 1, NULL, 0),
(460, 10, 83, 'service', 'Alcohol-based Liquid', '<p>Alcohol-based liquids are widely used for disinfection, sanitization, and medical applications due to their strong antimicrobial properties. Typically containing ethanol, isopropyl alcohol, or a combination of both (60-90%), they effectively eliminate bacteria, viruses, and fungi on surfaces and skin.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743412163_sanitizer.jpg', 1, NULL, 0),
(461, 10, 83, 'service', 'Sanitizing Wipes', '<p>Sanitizing wipes are pre-moistened disposable wipes infused with antibacterial and antiviral agents, commonly containing alcohol or disinfectant solutions. They provide a quick and effective way to clean hands, surfaces, and objects, helping to eliminate 99.9% of germs, bacteria, and viruses.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743412248_paper.jpg', 1, NULL, 0),
(462, 10, 83, 'service', 'Hand Rubs', '<p>Hand rubs are alcohol-based antiseptic solutions designed to kill germs and bacteria instantly without the need for water. They are widely used in hospitals, workplaces, and homes to prevent the spread of infections.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743412323_hand-wash.jpg', 1, NULL, 0),
