(823, 17, 157, 'features', 'Most importantly shooting', '<p>Shooter games, or shooters,&quot; are&nbsp;a subgenre of action video games where the primary focus is on defeating enemies using ranged weapons, often in fast-paced and intense gameplay</p>', 'https://fontawesome.com/', 'Read More', '1743571312_featured_game_thumb05.jpg', 1, 2, 1),
