(854, 9, 160, 'blog', 'The whimsically named Egg Canvas brainchesiko', '<p>There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but majority have suffered teration in some form, by injected humour, or randomised words which don&#39;t look even slight believable. If you are going to use a passage of Lorem Ipsum.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743404485_post-1.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(855, 9, 160, 'blog', 'Budget Issues Force The Our To Become', '<p>In today&#39;s challenging economic climate, budget constraints are forcing individuals, businesses, and organizations to rethink their strategies. Rising costs, inflation, and financial uncertainties have made it necessary to adopt more efficient and cost-effective solutions.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743404603_post-2.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(856, 9, 160, 'blog', 'Enrich Your Mind Envision Your Future Education for Success', '<p>Education is the key to unlocking your true potential. It shapes your mind, builds your skills, and opens doors to endless opportunities. By investing in learning, you empower yourself to grow, adapt, and succeed in a constantly evolving world.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743404687_news-12.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(857, 9, 160, 'blog', 'Exploring The Green Spaces Of Realar Residence', '<p>Realar Residence is more than just a place to live&mdash;it&#39;s a sanctuary of greenery, offering residents a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life. Designed with nature in mind, the lush landscapes, well-maintained gardens, and serene walking paths create a perfect environment for relaxation and rejuvenation.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743404765_news-13.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(858, 9, 160, 'features', 'Step Back in Time at Ancient Ruins', '<p>Exploring ancient ruins is like traveling through history, uncovering stories of past civilizations and architectural marvels. These sites offer a glimpse into the cultural, artistic, and technological advancements of bygone eras. Here are some fascinating features that make ancient ruins a must-visit:</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743404922_30.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(859, 9, 160, 'features', 'Uncover Vibrant Culture and History in Lisbon, Portugal', '<p>Lisbon, the stunning capital of Portugal, is a city rich in culture, history, and charm. From its cobbled streets to its breathtaking viewpoints, Lisbon offers an unforgettable experience for travelers. Here are some standout features that make this city a must-visit destination:</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743405039_31.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(860, 9, 160, 'features', 'Marvel at Majestic Mountains and  Lakes in Banff, Canada', '<p>Nestled in the heart of the Canadian Rockies, Banff is a breathtaking destination known for its towering mountains, crystal-clear lakes, and stunning natural beauty. Here are some standout features that make Banff a must-visit place:</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743405141_29.jpg', 1, 6, 1),
(861, 9, 160, 'service', 'Families Tour', '<p>Embark on a memorable family tour filled with adventure, relaxation, and bonding moments. Whether exploring vibrant cities, enjoying theme parks, or immersing in nature, family trips create lifelong memories. Choose destinations that cater to all ages, from beach resorts to cultural heritage sites. Enjoy hassle-free travel with kid-friendly accommodations, exciting activities, and delicious local cuisine.</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743405333_icon-01.svg', 1, 6, 1),
(862, 9, 160, 'service', 'Bike Tours', '<p>Bike tours offer a thrilling way to explore scenic landscapes, historic cities, and breathtaking countryside routes. Whether cycling through rugged mountain trails, coastal roads, or charming villages, bike travel provides an immersive and eco-friendly adventure. Enjoy the freedom of open roads, discover hidden gems, and experience local culture up close</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743405591_icon-4.svg', 1, 6, 1),
(863, 9, 160, 'service', 'Night Tours', '<p>Night tours offer a unique way to explore cities, landscapes, and attractions under the enchanting glow of the evening lights. Whether strolling through illuminated streets, joining ghost tours, or enjoying breathtaking skyline views, nighttime travel provides a different perspective. Experience vibrant nightlife, cultural performances, or peaceful moonlit cruises</p>', '', 'Read More', '1743405662_icon-5.svg', 1, 6, 1);
